
- Requirements:

  - A C++ compiler with C++11 support.
    The following compilers have been tested:
    - GCC 4.8.2 (GNU/Linux x86_64).

  - Qt (tested with version 4.8.5).

  - Gnuspeech-SA.

  - Currently the sound is played using the program "aplay" from ALSA.

- Build Gnuspeech-SA, with source directory at ../gnuspeech_sa and
  build directory at ../gnuspeech_sa-build.

- Generate the Makefile (GNU/Linux):

  qmake "MOC_DIR=tmp" "OBJECTS_DIR=tmp"

- Build (GNU/Linux):

  make
